are driven by fear, not for that purpose.

85
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:52,799
His seemingly irrational approach

86
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:54,900
astonishingly resembles an episode from

87
00:03:52,799 --> 00:03:57,420
'Don Quixote.' Remember the moment when the

88
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:58,879
daring hidalgo himself, Don Quixote,

89
00:03:57,420 --> 00:04:02,220
aspires to emulate the noble knights of yore

90
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:04,019
